custom-meta.meta-value: All relevant data for this study can be found within the manuscript and its Supporting Information files. Due to the presence of potentially sensitive personal information in the data set, raw data from this study cannot be made publicly available for ethical reasons. However, specific aggregated data from this study can be made available on request, with the permission of the Malaysian Ministry of Health. To request access to additional data, please contact Ms Angelica Fiona Tan, Research Officer, at tanangelica91@gmail.com.
